[0.000, "o", "\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[0.005, "o", "List and view ServiceNow UI Form layouts.\r\n\r\nForms are defined by sys_ui_section records for a specific table and view.\r\nCore UI uses views like \"Default view\", while Workspaces use views like \"service operations workspace\".\r\n\r\nExamples:\r\n  jsn forms list --table incident\r\n  jsn forms show incident --view \"Default view\"\r\n  jsn forms show incident --view \"service operations workspace\"\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "Usage:\r\n  jsn forms [command]\r\n\r\nAliases:\r\n  forms, form\r\n\r\nAvailable Commands:\r\n  list        List form views for a table\r\n  show        Show form layout for a table\r\n\r\nFlags:\r\n  -h, --help   help for forms\r\n\r\nGlobal Flags:\r\n      --agent            Agent mode (JSON + quiet + no interactive prompts)\r\n      --config string    config file (default is $HOME/.config/servicenow/config.json)\r\n      --jq string        Apply jq filter to JSON output\r\n      --json             Output as JSON\r\n      --md               Output as Markdown\r\n      --no-interactive   Disable interactive prompts (for scripts/CI)\r\n  -p, --profile string   profile to use\r\n  -q, --quiet            Quiet output (data only, no envelope)\r\n\r\nUse \"jsn forms [command] --help\" for more information about a command.\r\n"]
